{"tid":600820,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[開不了口] 睇唔過眼幫朋友講","createTime":"2018-03-21T15:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T07:21:09.000Z","uid":1440,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a71ec588139ee682e70011a6f41e56d46790e4e6","tid":600820,"uid":1440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:56:20.000Z","msg":"話說我個由小學識到大既老死前幾日生日啦 我就同佢過左澳門有大玩大 其實條撚樣牛高馬大生人唔生膽 去到骨場俾幾千銀乜柒都冇做過 阿嫂你就唔好再為難佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條撚樣又係on9 條女又親手整蛋糕比你 又整卡比你 就擺明鐘意你啦 你男人老狗就大膽d啦 要咩面啫 咩開不了口啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿嫂都唔該主動d  唔好忽冷忽熱 講你就講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知你兩條友都有睇連登 擺到明講你兩個 快撚啲好返啦好嗎 再唔係我就搶走你條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申返真係我朋友"},{"pid":"80deda637bbcbb2e2d1c756354c9e740e350c0e0","tid":600820,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"我哋嘅私事唔使放上連登啩?"},{"pid":"68b50c2cdda0c54268996abe61ab467a5c4a3394","tid":600820,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5458dda212785e260ed0abb617c71a8ceb07dc1a","tid":600820,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"去到骨場俾幾千銀乜柒都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有你呢位老友真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee213a67d020c5f339f402887bb9feae4e6f8bf","tid":600820,"uid":1440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5458dda212785e260ed0abb617c71a8ceb07dc1a","tid":600820,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"去到骨場俾幾千銀乜柒都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有你呢位老友真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkg